'''처럼''' ''cheo.reom''
#like, as, as if 
#:[[이전]]'''처럼''' '''''Like''' before''
#:[[형제]] '''처럼''' '''''Like''' brothers''. 
#:[[개미]] '''처럼''' 부지런하다. '''''As''' hardworking '''as''' an ant''. 
#:내일 죽을것'''처럼''' 살아라. ''Live '''as if''' you will die tomorrow''.
#:나비처럼 날아서 벌처럼 쏘다. (''Nabi '''cheoreom''' naraseo beol '''cheoreom''' ssoda'') Fly '''like''' a butterfly, sting '''like''' a bee. 

